; Coverage for filters.cc POST_MUST_BALANCE via auto-virtualize
; When all postings are balanced virtual ([brackets]), subtotal reports
; should mark generated posts with POST_MUST_BALANCE

2024/01/01 Test A
    [Budget:Food]    $100.00
    [Budget:Savings]  $-100.00

2024/01/15 Test B
    [Budget:Food]     $50.00
    [Budget:Savings]   $-50.00

test reg --subtotal
24-Jan-01 - 24-Jan-15           [Budget:Food]               $150.00      $150.00
                                [Budget:Savings]           $-150.00            0
end test
